title: Fixes deprecated ENV key value format
`LegacyKeyValueFormat` in Gradle variants: update format
body:
```
[...]
 2 warnings found (use --debug to expand):
 - LegacyKeyValueFormat: "ENV key=value" should be used instead of legacy "ENV key value" format (line 17)
 - LegacyKeyValueFormat: "ENV key=value" should be used instead of legacy "ENV key value" format (line 18)
[...]
```

title: Set deterministic CTAN mirror via a configuration option
Add texlive 2025 as version (once it is released)
body:
https://www.tug.org/texlive/

```
Plan for TeX Live 2025:
1feb: candidate/final sources committed, test builds begin.
8feb: [TL pretest](https://www.tug.org/texlive/pretest.html) starts, CTAN updates continue there and in tlnet.
22feb: code freeze for final build, major bug fixes only.
1mar: final updates from CTAN, final doc tweaks.
8mar: release TL and MacTeX.
```

title: CI: integrate 2023 variant into build matrix
body:
As a follow-up of #35 and the related [commit](https://github.com/maxkratz/docker_texlive/commit/5d87e8bef919397c230ed0af414cda3e7599989a), [this GitHub Actions CI job](https://github.com/maxkratz/docker_texlive/blob/main/.github/workflows/build-and-push.yml#L62-L89) could easily be integrated into the build matrix.
Beforehand, the separation was necessary because the build matrix did not use self-hosted runners.
